  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective is to highlight, by functional imaging (MRI) dysfunctional brain regions
      associated with vulnerability to suicidal behavior.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
